&lt;/div>&lt;figcaption>
Gene Ontology Enrichment Analysis of &lt;em>crb2a -/-&lt;/em> retina transcrtipomes.
&lt;/figcaption>&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We hope to assess several &lt;em>CRB1&lt;/em> patients with different variants to give us an insight into how genetic differences within the same gene could result in the varied phenotype (LCA/RP).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
&lt;figure >
